author: jhardin
msg: Modify hit_frequencies to provide cross-reference data (e.g. ham rule overlap reports spam overlap% for that rule) to help find rules to meta with to reduce FPs (look for ham overlap rules having no spam overlap) without a lot of back-and-forth scrolling through the report

author: mxmanghi
msg: * src/apache-2/mod_rivet.c: static void ap_chdir_file renamed as static int Rivet_chdir_file. Rivet_chdir_file
returns the value returned by chdir. This value is checked and in case of error the request
aborts with an HTTP_INTERNAL_ERROR and a message is printed in the log file.
